Description:
    Builds the directory and configuration structure for new campaigns.

Example:
    rails generate campaign blah

    This will create:
        config/campaigns/blah.yml
        app/assets/javascripts/campaigns/blah
        app/assets/javascripts/campaigns/blah/application.js
        app/assets/javascripts/campaigns/blah/filters.js
        app/assets/stylesheets/campaigns/blah
        app/assets/stylesheets/campaigns/blah/application.sass
        app/views/campaigns/blah/
        app/views/campaigns/blah/popups/
